  "texts": [
    "Other notable tasks include question and answering systems (Venkataram et al. 2020), face recognition (Jain et al. 2007), and summarisation.",
    "The use of TM for the latter task is becoming more popular.",
    "For example, Rakrouki et al. (2023) proposed Topic Graph Summarizer (TG-SMR) for text summarisation.",
    "Joshi et al. (2023) proposed DeepSumm for text summarisation by embedding the topic information obtained using LDA in the sequence networks to generate the summary.",
    "In the OCR (optical character recognition) context, studies like Mutuvi et al. (2018) showed TM users should take caution when applying TM to OCR datasets as OCR errors negatively impacts TM performance."
  ],
